properties.property: local nb_times = 1 function npc_handler(npc, ch) do_message(npc, ch, "You know what?") do_message(npc, ch, string.format("I have already asked this question %d times today.", nb_times)) nb_times = nb_times + 1 do_npc_close(npc, ch) end
function npc_handler(npc, ch) do_message(npc, ch, "Don't you think the guy behind me is my evil twin?") do_npc_close(npc, ch) end

function npc_handler(npc, ch) local v = do_choice(npc, ch, "Buy", "Sell") if v == 1 then mana.npc_trade(npc, ch, false, { {525, 0, 800}, {531, 0, 3000}, {530, 0, 8000}, {1199, 0, 3} }) elseif v == 2 then mana.npc_trade(npc, ch, true, { {525, 0, 400}, {531, 0, 1500}, {530, 0, 4000}, {1199, 0, 1} }) end do_npc_close(npc, ch) end
function npc_handler(npc, ch) do_message(npc, ch, "This is really a nice place.\nDon't you think so?") do_npc_close(npc, ch) end
function npc_handler(npc, ch) do_message(npc, ch, "If I only had a tent...") do_npc_close(npc, ch) end
